news.title: Development started
news.author: Cubxity
content: Hello there folks! XMC launcher had started it's development, this launcher will supports multi gamespaces, versions and multiple instances at once
We've planned a LOT of features for the launcher, join Cubxity's discord for updates and more information regarding updates https://discord.gg/KhBDa2t
